# Required: Vercel AI Gateway API key. Routes Anthropic / OpenAI / etc.
# calls through the gateway so we don't bind the project to a specific
# provider's billing or rate limits. Generate one at:
#   https://vercel.com/dashboard -> AI Gateway -> API Keys
# In Vercel deploys this is set under Project Settings -> Environment
# Variables and is automatically injected into the lambdas.
AI_GATEWAY_API_KEY=
